Cook Gorton's Fish Fillets according to instructions on package. Melt butter in a large skillet. Crumble ramen noodles and add to skillet with almonds; cook, stirring constantly, until noodles are golden. Remove from pan; cool. Place oil, ramen seasoning packet, vinegar, and sugar in blender; cover. Blend until smooth. Combine salad greens, noodle mixture, green onions, Gorton's Fish Fillets and dressing in a large bowl. Toss to coat well. Serve immediately.